        "mainbody": "'''Morndin Gloomstorm''' was the high [[cleric]] of [[Laduguer]] in [[Gracklstugh]] in [[1370 DR]]",
        "History": "Morndin was born to [[Clan Bukbukken]], as the son of [[Kildor]] and blood of [[Balgor]], in [[Shimmergloom]]'s Run in [[Mithral Hall]]. Morndin lived under the [[shadow dragon]] Shimmergloom's rule until the [[shield dwarf|shield dwarves]] of [[Clan Battlehammer]] reclaimed their ancestral home. He was one of the few surviving members of his clan to manage to escape to Gracklstugh. There, Morndin become high priest of the local temple of Laduguer."
